    {"type":"text","id":"wb_t","x":444,"y":662,"width":582,"height":140,"text":"S4 WRITEBACK — the feedback IS the gate\n\nissue CAS →  dqFree = gc+lat+BL2 ;  next_cas_any = gc+tCCD_S ;\n             next_cas_bg = gc+tCCD_L ;  next_pre[b] = MAX(…, gc+tRTP/tWR)\n\n⇒ next cycle can_cas DEASSERTS for the burst window\n⇒ 3 of the 4 CA slots free ⇒ arbiter spends them on ACT/PRE prep\n   for OTHER banks ⇒ their CAS legal when DQ frees ⇒ DQ stays full.","originalText":"S4 WRITEBACK — the feedback IS the gate\n\nissue CAS →  dqFree = gc+lat+BL2 ;  next_cas_any = gc+tCCD_S ;\n             next_cas_bg = gc+tCCD_L ;  next_pre[b] = MAX(…, gc+tRTP/tWR)\n\n⇒ next cycle can_cas DEASSERTS for the burst window\n⇒ 3 of the 4 CA slots free ⇒ arbiter spends them on ACT/PRE prep\n   for OTHER banks ⇒ their CAS legal when DQ frees ⇒ DQ stays full.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#7c2d12","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":400032,"version":1,"versionNonce":400033,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":"wb","lineHeight":1.35},

